        "title": "Operador flecha",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 103001,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Aprendamos cómo crear <strong>arrow functions</strong>. Son parte del estándar ES6 de JavaScript y se utilizan para escribir código más limpio y corto.</p><p>Reescribamos la función a continuación como una función flecha usando solo una línea de código.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Hello'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Hi'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getGreeting());\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(greeting());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"72\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hi\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>const greeting = () =&gt; 'Hi';</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Anonymous Function",
            "id": 103846,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Las funciones flecha son un tipo de <strong>función</strong><strong>anónima</strong>, lo que significa que no tienen un nombre de función.</p><p>Si queremos llamar a estas funciones, necesitamos almacenarlas dentro de una variable y llamar a la variable con paréntesis al final.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings!'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Hi'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getGreeting());\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(greeting());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"63\" /><option startIndex=\"64\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option startIndex=\"131\" endIndex=\"141\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Greetings!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hi\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>const greeting</code> seguido de <code>=</code> y finalmente <code>greeting()</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parentheses",
            "id": 103847,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Con las funciones flecha, no necesitamos la palabra clave <code>function</code> ni el nombre de la función. Eso significa que lo primero que comenzamos es con paréntesis.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings!'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option startIndex=\"67\" endIndex=\"68\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>(</code> seguido de <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parameter",
            "id": 103848,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Al igual que con las funciones normales, podemos agregar parámetros dentro de los paréntesis y luego usar los parámetros dentro de la función.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getGreeting\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"firstName\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + firstName;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greeting = \" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"firstName\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + firstName;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(greeting(\" /><text value=\"'Tony'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"));\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"88\" endIndex=\"97\" /><option startIndex=\"127\" endIndex=\"136\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Greetings Tony\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>firstName</code> seguido de <code>firstName</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Arrow operator",
            "id": 103004,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Justo después de los paréntesis y antes de la llave de apertura es donde añadimos el operador flecha <code>=&gt;</code>.</p><p>Usamos este operador justo antes del bloque de código o expresión que queremos que la función ejecute.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" hello = \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"myfunction\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings!'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" helloArrowFunction = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(hello());\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(helloArrowFunction());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"93\" endIndex=\"95\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Greetings!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Greetings \" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>=&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Multiple body statements",
            "id": 103005,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Al igual que con las funciones tradicionales, usamos llaves <code>{}</code> para contener el bloque de código de una función flecha.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" name = \" /><text value=\"'Elizabeth'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings '\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + name;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>{</code> seguido de <code>};</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "One body statement",
            "id": 103006,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Si una función flecha solo tiene una declaración, podemos omitir tanto las llaves como la palabra clave <code>return</code> para obtener un código muy corto.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"'Greetings'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{ return 'Greetings' }\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>'Greetings'</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Arrow operator",
            "id": 103700,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Dónde añadimos el operador flecha <code>=&gt;</code>?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Después de los paréntesis y antes de la llave de apertura</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Después de la palabra clave <code>function</code> y antes de la llave de apertura <code>{</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Después de los paréntesis y antes de la llave de apertura.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Multiple body statements",
            "id": 103701,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué hacen las llaves <code>{}</code> en una función flecha?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Contienen el bloque de código</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Se utilizan para llamar a una función</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Contienen el bloque de código.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: One body statement",
            "id": 103702,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo podemos acortar el siguiente código?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Al eliminar las llaves <code>{}</code> y la palabra clave <code>return</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Eliminando los paréntesis <code>()</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Al eliminar las llaves <code>{}</code> y la palabra clave <code>return</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Calling the function",
            "id": 103704,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo llamamos a la siguiente función flecha?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greetings = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" position = \" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello Jane!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>greetings();</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>greetings;</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>greetings();</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Parenthesis",
            "id": 103706,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Completa la función flecha.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getVehicleCount = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count = \" /><text value=\"4003\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getVehicleCount());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"26\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"var\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4003\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>(</code> seguido de <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Arrow operator",
            "id": 103707,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Codifica el operador flecha, <code>=&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getVehiclesCount = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count = \" /><text value=\"4003\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" count;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"};\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getVehiclesCount());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"30\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4003\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>=&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: One body statement",
            "id": 103709,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Haz que la función devuelva el valor <code>400</code> escribiendo la función flecha más corta posible.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getVehiclesCount = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"400\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getVehiclesCount());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"30\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"return\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"400\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>()</code> seguido de <code>=&gt;</code> y finalmente <code>400</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Calling the function",
            "id": 103711,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Llama a la función flecha.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" getMessage = \" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" =&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to Cyprus!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(getMessage());\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"59\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option startIndex=\"69\" endIndex=\"70\" /><option startIndex=\"70\" endIndex=\"71\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Welcome to Cyprus!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>getMessage</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
      }
